dmca.title: DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google
dmca.sender_name: Squidoo Lens - Sweet Things to Say to Your Boyfriend

works.description:
This Blogger page simply copied my entire
 
page from Squidoo, including text format, text content, and html and gave 

no reference back to me or notification to me.

Also, their copy includes the photos of products I am an affiliate for  
(with no links to show this of course).
